\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:composition-of-psi-p-and-get-simplified"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

), if only we could move these functions next to each other.
