 Typically, that is done by naturality laws.
 By analogy with Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:naturality-law-of-filter"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

